{"tid":38490,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[其實唔難]紫薯牛奶包","createTime":"2016-12-14T03:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T15:12:22.000Z","uid":4456,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b38cf42af5379128a854e3c0d22ca1571232000a","tid":38490,"uid":4456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:10:39.000Z","msg":"好耐都無係高登貼過食譜, 黎到呢度決定貼一個我覺得唔難但又幾好食既麵包食譜開心share <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i0.wp.com/vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/04/dscf0693.jpg?ssl=1&amp;w=450\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F04%2Fdscf0693.jpg%3Fssl%3D1%26w%3D450&h=ff0f4a51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFB: <a href=\"http://vlovecooking.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecooking.com%2F&d=g1lacP68hShYVP6FbE%2FDJEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=bb163c08\" target=\"_blank\">http://vlovecooking.com/</a><br />\nblog: <a href=\"https://vlovecooking.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvlovecooking.com%2F&d=g1lacP68hShYVP6FbE%2FDJEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=c9f8fe40\" target=\"_blank\">https://vlovecooking.com/</a>"},{"pid":"0d3f7d37b7aa935edb978027ef1190135d843846","tid":38490,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:11:35.000Z","msg":"好似唔錯"},{"pid":"26f146a03960a7edf6dd8a1fac5bc7ab5efb55a2","tid":38490,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:11:41.000Z","msg":"<em><ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">極邪惡</span></span></strong></ins></em>"},{"pid":"584708330c2e80c2ee5e5b6ee100981aaa1a3035","tid":38490,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:12:19.000Z","msg":"好邪惡啊"},{"pid":"27910955eb141e5060aa7ad78bfd162142a2562a","tid":38490,"uid":4456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:14:42.000Z","msg":"材料:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/04/img_3317.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F04%2Fimg_3317.jpg&h=73d91324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>麵團</ins></span></span>\t<br />\n<br />\n牛奶 140ml<br />\n高筋麵粉 250g<br />\n紫薯蓉 100g<br />\n砂糖 40g<br />\n鹽 3g<br />\n速發酵母 3g<br />\n椰子油 20g<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/04/img_3320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F04%2Fimg_3320.jpg&h=409126f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">紫薯餡</span></ins></span><br />\n紫薯蓉 150g<br />\n牛奶 60ml<br />\n砂糖 15g"},{"pid":"c9e32d880b9bfb03299a7bbce8a1e043b9babc0e","tid":38490,"uid":4456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:17:38.000Z","msg":"做法<br />\n<br />\n1) 紫薯去皮洗淨切細粒蒸熟後, 用叉壓成蓉<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">(留起當中100g 加入麵團)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/04/img_3315.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F04%2Fimg_3315.jpg&h=31fc1459&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2) 麵團材料混合好, 搓至光滑不黏手及可撐出薄膜, 取出滾圓放入容器內, 蓋上濕布或保鮮紙, 發酵至2倍大(約1小時)-<span style=\"color: red;\"> 第1次發酵<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/04/img_3325.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F04%2Fimg_3325.jpg&h=0871289c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3) <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第1次發酵</span></span> 完成後取出麵團, 平均分成6等份(約88g)<br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/04/img_3326.jpg?w=496&amp;h=372&amp;crop=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F04%2Fimg_3326.jpg%3Fw%3D496%26h%3D372%26crop%3D1&h=25d3d086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/04/img_3327.jpg?w=496&amp;h=372&amp;crop=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F04%2Fimg_3327.jpg%3Fw%3D496%26h%3D372%26crop%3D1&h=4b5fcbc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07993854c4f700c07244fc48b5db1db73240a8e7","tid":38490,"uid":4456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:18:54.000Z","msg":"4)  桿平麵團後加入紫薯餡包好滾圓, 用保鮮紙或濕巾蓋好, 放置30分鐘-<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第2次發酵</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/04/img_3328.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F04%2Fimg_3328.jpg&h=93743d4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5) 之後可按喜好掃上雞蛋(上色用)或鋪上芝麻(裝飾用), 放入己預熱190&deg;c 焗爐焗16分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/04/img_3334.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F04%2Fimg_3334.jpg&h=d3a03c41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"510dd46bff674266ac576df805e7fe692a8549d3","tid":38490,"uid":4456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:23:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><em><ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">極邪惡</span></span></strong></ins></em></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個餡我無落牛油, 邪惡度-50"},{"pid":"b59de3bf7b43e798968e505f0fc600ea1dd51c77","tid":38490,"uid":58246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:40:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好耐都無係高登貼過食譜, 黎到呢度決定貼一個我覺得唔難但又幾好食既麵包食譜開心share <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i0.wp.com/vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/04/dscf0693.jpg?ssl=1&amp;amp;w=450\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F04%2Fdscf0693.jpg%3Fssl%3D1%26amp%3Bw%3D450&h=263e6ff9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFB: <a href=\"http://vlovecooking.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecooking.com%2F&d=g1lacP68hShYVP6FbE%2FDJEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=bb163c08\" target=\"_blank\">http://vlovecooking.com/</a><br />\nblog: <a href=\"https://vlovecooking.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvlovecooking.com%2F&d=g1lacP68hShYVP6FbE%2FDJEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=c9f8fe40\" target=\"_blank\">https://vlovecooking.com/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似好乾咁既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"607351c505ac86b357063d8338226f3a02050cbf","tid":38490,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:51:03.000Z","msg":"賣相贏晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d6c874366561bb5986dca514279d1b4241fbb2","tid":38490,"uid":4456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:00:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好耐都無係高登貼過食譜, 黎到呢度決定貼一個我覺得唔難但又幾好食既麵包食譜開心share <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i0.wp.com/vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/04/dscf0693.jpg?ssl=1&amp;w=450\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F04%2Fdscf0693.jpg%3Fssl%3D1%26w%3D450&h=ff0f4a51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFB: <a href=\"http://vlovecooking.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecooking.com%2F&d=g1lacP68hShYVP6FbE%2FDJEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=bb163c08\" target=\"_blank\">http://vlovecooking.com/</a><br />\nblog: <a href=\"https://vlovecooking.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvlovecooking.com%2F&d=g1lacP68hShYVP6FbE%2FDJEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=c9f8fe40\" target=\"_blank\">https://vlovecooking.com/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似好乾咁既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔算好乾, 但又唔係濕到一PAT野咁囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n質地似杰杰地既薯蓉<br />\n如果怕乾可以落多少少奶撈既"},{"pid":"fc31e5bf38f4668389c1a00f306825ac6c4b96db","tid":38490,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:02:02.000Z","msg":"冇拉絲"},{"pid":"e59db308aa6754c93ebf806a2fc09abf87b69155","tid":38490,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T10:48:26.000Z","msg":"男仔見到都留口水"},{"pid":"14923976f2372ba43d5c4c8a368a523744ae73b9","tid":38490,"uid":11236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:03:31.000Z","msg":"傳說中隱世紫薯牛奶包 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41d95ca6f8a47355f7c5ac4b2576b65ccaaccf1","tid":38490,"uid":51446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:05:20.000Z","msg":"隱世小店，超邪惡&hellip;"},{"pid":"63f50266d8142b0448076c532daede0f3f806c9e","tid":38490,"uid":9152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:07:04.000Z","msg":"抹茶呢...炸雞呢...？"},{"pid":"51ca9efceb8ead70eba95e5f2d6e7c734abc93c8","tid":38490,"uid":32462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:12:01.000Z","msg":"極邪惡期間限定日式流心爆漿紫薯牛奶包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d000dadc44c46fd0a0b50ba373bd1e38d3be88a6","tid":38490,"uid":8174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T12:00:06.000Z","msg":"樓主個包屌打出面啲垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.pn